## GITOPS R2 database backup rollout (2026-07-14)

- Implemented and deployed the governed `CloudMCP -> GitOps -> Cloudapi assets -> R2` logical-backup path, 30-day retention cleanup, checksum manifest, distinct-target restore contract, and Cloudapi asset deletion; no direct R2/S3 credentials or endpoint were added.
